00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:29,020
you know I'm innocent,

863
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:30,340
so why are you locking me up?

864
00:41:30,820 --> 00:41:31,780
Bao Chenyan,

865
00:41:32,580 --> 00:41:33,780
I've already said it.

866
00:41:33,900 --> 00:41:35,180
Today is just a casual chat,

867
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:36,900
not a formal interrogation.

868
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:45,140
Xing Liang!

869
00:41:45,780 --> 00:41:47,180
Xing Liang, let's talk some more!

870
00:42:22,470 --> 00:42:25,980
The moon is surrounded by stars

871
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:30,410
I hide my regrets in the dark

872
00:42:31,170 --> 00:42:33,230
You said don't go

873
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:38,770
Because that's where you belong

874
00:42:41,030 --> 00:42:44,590
Wild winds blow across the land

875
00:42:45,050 --> 00:42:49,100
Witnessing the hardships
we've been through

876
00:42:49,810 --> 00:42:52,130
You said don't be afraid

877
00:42:52,130 --> 00:42:56,680
Even though life is always hard

878
00:42:57,830 --> 00:42:59,750
Looking back

879
00:42:59,750 --> 00:43:02,410
My laughters and tears

880
00:43:02,410 --> 00:43:04,310
You've seen them all

881
00:43:04,310 --> 00:43:07,010
I've loved, got hurt, and made mistakes

882
00:43:07,010 --> 00:43:08,990
Maybe it's in the past

883
00:43:08,990 --> 00:43:10,550
Still remember

884
00:43:11,120 --> 00:43:16,350
The promises I made

885
00:43:16,850 --> 00:43:18,380
Dream about those years

886
00:43:18,380 --> 00:43:21,060
Waking up feeling painful

887
00:43:21,060 --> 00:43:23,050
On those lonely nights

888
00:43:23,050 --> 00:43:25,720
I couldn't sleep

889
00:43:25,720 --> 00:43:27,690
Praying for a good ending

890
00:43:27,690 --> 00:43:29,430
All that's left

891
00:43:29,430 --> 00:43:34,530
Is a sigh

892
00:43:41,620 --> 00:43:43,080
How I wish

893
00:43:43,700 --> 00:43:50,230
I could see you again
